dag score
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:the extent to which a sheep produces dags or dungy wool in relation to weight gain.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
