Source: Taranaki Daily News
Author:
Vol / Page: 21
Edition:
Quote: He charted the amount of dags against weight gain, finding a very even correlation - more dags, less weight gain, and a high correlation between dag score and Wormfree blood tests run by MAF, Invermay.
